# meta-toradex-avt
Support layer for Allied Vision Alvium CSI cameras on toradex hardware.

## Compatibility
This release is tested with:
- Toradex Verdin iMX8M Plus + Toradex Mallow Carrier 

## Dependencies

This layer depends on:
 - meta-toradex-nxp
 - meta-alvium-avt

## Maintainers, Mailing list, Patches

For any patches or pull requests please use the Github pull requests.
For comments or questions about this layer, please create an issue or contact support@alliedvision.com.

Maintainers:

	Dennis Langenkamp


